<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is not a story. This book consists of faq about autism and author answering them. It is really helpful if you want to know more about people with<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is not a story. This book consists of faq about autism and author answering them. It is really helpful if you want to know more about people with autism. This book finally answered some questions I had about my brother (he can't speak nor write) so I definitely recommend.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
